Description: 宋佩芬：毕加索的名人魅力自然不容忽视，但马拉加毕加索博物馆却相信，自身的可持续发展不能仅仅依赖“毕加索故乡”这一张招牌。

Images: ["[000183521_pic...](https://thumbor.ftacademy.cn/unsafe/picture/1/000183521_piclink.jpg)", "[000183542_pic...](https://thumbor.ftacademy.cn/unsafe/picture/2/000183542_piclink.jpg)", "[000183523_pic...](https://thumbor.ftacademy.cn/unsafe/picture/3/000183523_piclink.jpg)", "[000183526_pic...](https://thumbor.ftacademy.cn/unsafe/picture/6/000183526_piclink.png)", "[000183524_pic...](https://thumbor.ftacademy.cn/unsafe/picture/4/000183524_piclink.jpg)"]

